43
00:04:32,140 --> 00:04:44,349
Is your city bustling or sleepy? If a town
is sleepy there’s not much activity and

44
00:04:44,350 --> 00:04:45,760
things are quiet.

45
00:04:45,760 --> 00:04:49,093
