81
00:08:53,310 --> 00:08:58,410
Part four: saying what you dislike.

82
00:08:58,410 --> 00:09:04,269
Let’s look at some examples which express
negative feelings:

83
00:09:04,269 --> 00:09:14,820
"Paris is great, but the cost of living is
really high. That can be quite stressful because

84
00:09:14,820 --> 00:09:18,730
you’re always thinking about money and how
to make ends meet."

85
00:09:18,730 --> 00:09:30,399
"Shanghai’s an exciting place, but it’s
really crowded and it can be exhausting to

86
00:09:30,399 --> 00:09:36,149
live there. Air quality can be an issue, particularly
in the summer."

87
00:09:36,149 --> 00:09:43,060
"Banbury’s nice, but sometimes I find it
a bit boring. There’s not much nightlife

88
00:09:43,060 --> 00:09:50,979
and sometimes it feels a 
bit cut off from the wider world."

89
00:09:50,980 --> 00:10:01,370
When talking about things you don’t like
about your hometown, you can use adjectives

90
00:10:01,370 --> 00:10:04,339
like, 'stressful', 'crowded', 'boring'.

91
00:10:04,339 --> 00:10:13,350
You can make your answer more interesting
by using phrases. We saw some useful ones

92
00:10:13,350 --> 00:10:14,509
in our examples:

93
00:10:14,509 --> 00:10:23,980
"The cost of living is really high"; "You’re
always thinking about how to make ends meet."

94
00:10:23,980 --> 00:10:31,069
Meaning: you’re always thinking about how
to pay for your basic living costs.

95
00:10:31,069 --> 00:10:41,019
"It can be exhausting to live there"; "Air
quality can be an issue"; "There’s not much

96
00:10:41,019 --> 00:10:50,500
nightlife"; "It feels a bit cut off from the
wider world." Meaning: you feel like you’re

97
00:10:50,500 --> 00:10:54,300
far away from people, culture and activity.

98
00:10:54,300 --> 00:11:01,008
Could you use any of these phrases to describe
your hometown?

99
00:11:01,009 --> 00:11:09,769
Remember that you can also change the phrases
to fit your ideas. For example:

100
00:11:09,769 --> 00:11:21,449
"Traffic can be an issue"; "There’s not
much for young people to do"; "It can be very

101
00:11:21,449 --> 00:11:24,019
