115
00:12:50,769 --> 00:13:00,410
"Shanghai is almost unrecognisable compared
to twenty or thirty years ago. The city has

116
00:13:00,410 --> 00:13:10,420
expanded so much, both physically and economically.
It’s amazing when you see old photos of

117
00:13:10,420 --> 00:13:14,329
the city; things are so different now!"

118
00:13:14,329 --> 00:13:24,378
"Banbury hasn’t changed much as a place
in the last twenty years, but the mix of people

119
00:13:24,379 --> 00:13:33,519
is a bit different nowadays. The population
used to be older and mostly English, whereas

120
00:13:33,519 --> 00:13:42,779
now there are more young people living here,
including many people from other parts of

121
00:13:42,779 --> 00:13:43,779
Europe."

122
00:13:43,779 --> 00:13:51,290
